- Objective (same as prior): minimize `n_sis = n*d` first, then minimize overshoot above 128 bits.
- Search space: `b in {2,4,8}`, `k in [4,40]`, `K = floor((b^k-1)/(T(b-1))) - k`, earliest `n` meeting `sec >= 128`.
