- For `d=256`: use power-of-two cyclotomic `eta=512`, with `T_sparse_l1 = 23` (`alpha=1`)
- For `d=512`: use power-of-two cyclotomic `eta=1024`, with `T_sparse_l1 = 19` (`alpha=1`)

